{"tid":2446323,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港有錢人因政治動盪將資金大幅移轉至新加坡，新加坡非居民存款達3713億元 創新高","createTime":"2021-03-14T11:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T11:49:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f691a2baf54b47a0f75b2394bef93c70a6d9912","tid":2446323,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XXzBVOCFV4PeC.Gar24SFQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1OS42OTIzMDc2OTIzMDc3O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/.HrHik98MuyP1VG6XdKUvg--~B/aD01MzY7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/40557901615ed0035161a782971b247b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXXzBVOCFV4PeC.Gar24SFQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1OS42OTIzMDc2OTIzMDc3O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.HrHik98MuyP1VG6XdKUvg--~B%2FaD01MzY7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F40557901615ed0035161a782971b247b&h=570e208a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外地媒體報道，香港亞洲金融地位逐漸黯淡，新加坡看到龐大商機，祭出低稅率政策，包括香港在內的有錢人紛紛將資金轉移陣地。據最新統計，新加坡1月非居民存款直飆至642億坡元(約3,713億港元)，按年增20%，創下新高。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，香港有錢人因政治動盪將資金大幅移轉至新加坡，在2020年4月和5月，短短一個月，存款按年增長了40%以上。"},{"pid":"d061010cbde59af4f53fbfca92dedbd493aa943f","tid":2446323,"uid":997,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:11:21.000Z","msg":"應該係中資d錢黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addd0f6f6e91e710ce2e6a04f249f91c32b65573","tid":2446323,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:11:44.000Z","msg":"咁少"},{"pid":"68b5c84925149677b5ef0d81132f1314048803f5","tid":2446323,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"addd0f6f6e91e710ce2e6a04f249f91c32b65573","tid":2446323,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":